				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/C%C3%BAc-%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Khai-Nguy%C3%AAn-qu%C3%A1n-T%E1%BB%B1-L%E1%BA%A1c-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-ki%E1%BB%81u-c%C6%B0-nh%C3%A2n-th%E1%BB%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-vrzHPTYPKsNCKYUcc7a6xQ">Cúc Đường đề Khai Nguyên quán Tự Lạc tiên sinh kiều cư, nhân thứ kỳ vận - 菊堂題開元觀自樂先生僑居，因次其韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-S%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/author-jcnyctA2yI9a8upP-Bt9aw">Nguyễn Sưởng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Du-Ti%C3%AAn-L%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-v%C4%83n-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%A0m-Th%C3%A1i-Nguy%C3%AAn-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-chi-th%E1%BA%AFng-tu%C3%BD-h%E1%BA%ADu-th%C3%A0nh-ng%C3%A2m/poem-brX0JwY5PNTxSGgywPw-YQ">Du Tiên Lữ động văn nhân đàm Thái Nguyên sơn thuỷ chi thắng, tuý hậu thành ngâm - 遊仙侶洞聞人談太原山水之勝醉後成吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thanh-qu%C3%A1n/poem-L88Ll2l7WO22jksLbepoaA">Đề Ngọc Thanh quán - 題玉清館</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Ho%E1%BA%A1-Xu%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-PfULsBhN0m55_P51ZrFDIA">Hoạ Xuân Đài tức cảnh thi kỳ 2 - 和春臺即景詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-5/poem-5naBD3Q6Hp98_pkF_DgovA">Hữu cảm kỳ 5 - 有感其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="ht